---
import Navbar from "./navbar.astro";
---

<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>Overview</title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <Navbar />
    
    <section class="overview-section">
      <div class="overview-container">
        <div class="overview-header" data-aos="fade-up">
          <h1>Overview of Tunisian Governorates</h1>
          <p>Comprehensive regional data and insights</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="overview-content">
          <div class="overview-card" data-aos="fade-right">
            <h2>About This Platform</h2>
            <p>This platform provides detailed demographic and administrative data about the governorates of Tunisia. You can explore population numbers, geographical area, current governors, and more.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="overview-card" data-aos="fade-left">
            <h2>Data Sources</h2>
            <p>The goal is to offer a clean and accessible way to view, compare, and analyze regional statistics sourced from official datasets like <a href="https://data.gov.tn" target="_blank">data.gov.tn</a> and other reliable sources.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="overview-card" data-aos="fade-right">
            <h2>How to Use</h2>
            <p>Use the navigation menu to browse governorate profiles, view population charts, and access data sources. Each governorate card provides key information at a glance.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="overview-card" data-aos="fade-left">
            <h2>Contact Us</h2>
            <p>Have questions or suggestions? Visit our <a href="/contact">contact page</a> to get in touch with our team. We welcome feedback and contributions.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </body>
</html>

<style>
  .overview-section {
    background-color: var(--bg);
    min-height: calc(100vh - 70px);
    padding: 4rem 2rem;
  }

  .overview-container {
    max-width: 1000px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .overview-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .overview-header h1 {
    color: var(--primary);
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .overview-header p {
    color: var(--light-text);
    font-size: 1.2rem;
  }

  .overview-content {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(400px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .overview-card {
    background: white;
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 2rem;
    box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
  }

  .overview-card h2 {
    color: var(--primary);
    margin-top: 0;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
  }

  .overview-card p {
    color: var(--text);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .overview-card a {
    color: var(--secondary);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .overview-card a:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .overview-content {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
    
    .overview-header h1 {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }
  }
</style>